Applications

1. Information on Social Media

Research Question: What are peoples perceptions on Fertilty?

Twitter Data

  • Parse Tweets with keywords relevant to fertility (e.g.babies, diapers, baby shower, breastfeeding)
  • Positive/negative?
  • Objective/subjective?
  • Determine gender using users name
  • Time and day of tweet
  • Device info

2. Combining Traditional Data with New Sources of Information

Research Question: How does access to transportation relate to spatial inequality?

COTA Bus Lines

  • 120+ Bus lines and 3200+ bus stops
  • Matrix
  • Network analysis
  • Combine with food desert/income/race data

Bus Network

3. Using Technology to get Data

Research Question: Are user-based rating systems (e.g.Uber, Lyft, Airbnb) fair?

Airbnb Data

  • 250,000+ Airbnb listings in 28 US cities
  • Host picture
  • face recognition
  • skin color information (RGB, HSV, YCrCb, LAB)
  • Machine learning (scale 1-5)
  • text analysis (NLP)

Variables

  • skin tone
  • price of house
  • superhost?
  • number of reviews?
  • expected rating based on text reviews
